      "description": "optimized kagura build after nerf\n\nwhat can be changed?\ngenius wand for one shots early game (lvl 6 - 7)\nglowing wand can be changed with sky piercer, recommend glowing wand for heavy life stealers or healers (ruby, thaumuz..)\nlightning truncheon can be changed with wishing lantern if enemies are tanky and can sustain lots of damage\ndivine glaive can be changed with other items ex: blood wings, queens wings etc\nmagic crystal shouldn't be changed AT ALL always keep as your 5th or last item.\n\nemblems\ninspire for a total of 10% cd on emblem, 20% cd in total with truncheon or wishing lantern\nweapon master for extra damage \nif you want to maximize her damage further with emblems, switch inspire with rupture for adaptive penetration and/or war cry for 8% more damage, impure rage for extra mana and damage to tanks\nuse lethal ignition for finishers, very good when paired up with glowing wand\n\nbattle spells\nflicker, and flameshot are all good items for kagura\npetrify is also very underated\n\nall done!\n\n\n\n\n",
